title: Index of Production of Producers' Goods for United States
notes:
These Index Figures Are On A Daily Average Output Basis. Data For April-September 1939 Exclude Shipbuilding. Source: Data For 1919-1933: Directly From Dr. Y. S. Leong, Division Of Research And Planning, Nra. Data For 1934-1939: Directly From Dr. G. W. Hervey, Consumers' Counsel Division, Agricultural Adjustment Administration.

This NBER data series m01055 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
